ygData.messageBody:
Hey guys and gals. Hail and Well met.<br>My name
is Fred Zeppelin, I am a Warrior on the M-T server.
I have tried other classes but I like just slashing
and killing, I prefer to have to clean my armour at
the end of the day, to see my foe face to face as I
kill them <EG>. I currently have to running
Characters <br>Fred Zeppelin 23 rd yr Warrior of Qeynos
belonging to the Brother Gibborim<br>And<br>Fapherd 9th
season Barbarian Warrior of Halas.<br>I haveone other
character, but not sure how much I will play him he is a
Bard I created with just a little more RP, but like I
said Iam not sure how much I will play him.<br>SO
thats me in a nut shell. is anyone else her playing on
the M-T server?, if so let me know.
